videos.description: Kofi Cockburn gets the hoop on one end then comes up big on the defensive end as he spikes a shot out of bounds that hypes up the crowd and the Illinois bench.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Kofi Cockburn gets the bucket and a huge block to hype the crowd) 2021/12/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kofi Cockburn gets the bucket and a huge block to hype the crowd

videos.description: Arizona comes away with an 83-79 win over Illinois as Bennedict Mathurin goes 5-for-8 from downtown and racks up 30 points.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Bennedict Mathurin gets hot in Arizona's win) 2021/12/11 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Bennedict Mathurin gets hot in Arizona's win

videos.description: Alfonso Plummer is called for a costly 5-second violation after an inbounds pass that sets Arizona up for an 83-79 win over Illinois.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Illinois' Alfonso Plummer's makes costly violation late in the 2nd half) 2021/12/11 ESHEET

videos.headline: Illinois' Alfonso Plummer's makes costly violation late in the 2nd half
